#

Pan-Seared New York Steak with Mushroom Bordelaise and Creamy Polenta

$35
800 kcal
Difficulty: 70%

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

GourmetSteakComfort Food

Description

Succulent New York steak seared to perfection, paired with rich mushroom bordelaise and creamy polenta for a gourmet experience.

Ingredients

  • New York Strip Steak: 2 (8 oz) pieces
  • Mushrooms (cremini or shiitake): 2 cups, sliced
  • Red wine: 1 cup
  • Beef stock: 1 cup
  • Shallots: 1/2 cup, minced
  • Butter: 4 tablespoons
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Polenta: 1 cup
  • Heavy cream: 1/2 cup
  • Parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup, grated
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Fresh thyme: 1 tablespoon, chopped
